        "note": {
          "en": "I2C control bus shared with XL9555; ES8388 at I2C address 0x20. Speaker enable is via the XL9555 IO expander.",
          "zh-CN": "I2C 控制总线与 XL9555 共用；ES8388 的 I2C 地址为 0x20。喇叭使能由 XL9555 IO 扩展芯片控制。"
        }
      }
    ],
