        {
          "deviceClass": "touchpad",
          "interface": "I2C",
          "pins": {
            "I2C": [
              {
                "role": "scl",
                "gpio": 38
              },
              {
                "role": "sda",
                "gpio": 39
              },
              {
                "role": "int",
                "gpio": 40
              },
              {
                "role": "rst",
                "expanderId": "io-expander-xl9555",
                "expanderPin": 9
              }
            ]
          }
        }
      ],
      "note": {
        "en": "One 40-pin connector carrying both the RGB display and its capacitive touch (data/DE/PCLK on fixed MCU GPIOs; backlight/reset via XL9555). RGB data pins are shared with the DVP camera header and the on-board I2S audio. Attach one compatible RGB-touch panel; generate its driver for these exact pins.",
        "zh-CN": "同一个 40 脚接插件,同时引出 RGB 显示与电容触摸(数据/DE/PCLK 走固定 MCU GPIO;背光/复位经 XL9555)。RGB 数据脚与 DVP 摄像头排针、板载 I2S 音频共用。接一块兼容的带触摸 RGB 屏,按这组固定脚生成驱动。"
      }
    },
