            ]
          }
        }
      ],
      "note": {
        "en": "OV2640-class DVP camera header; no XCLK broken out. SCCB (i2c_scl=IO38/i2c_sda=IO39) shared with the touch I2C; data pins shared with the RGB LCD header. PWDN/RESET via XL9555 (#4/#5).",
        "zh-CN": "OV2640 类 DVP 摄像头排针;未引出 XCLK。SCCB(i2c_scl=IO38/i2c_sda=IO39)与触摸 I2C 共用;数据脚与 RGB LCD 排针共用。PWDN/复位经 XL9555(#4/#5)。"
      }
